OL,5,G0600 Teleshopping
OL,6,     FShop by phone from the comfort of
OL,7,     Fyour home.
OL,8,G0700 Shop: Thane Offers
OL,9,     FVisit Thane.tv and browse our
OL,10,     Fselection of award winning home
OL,11,     Fand fitness products that let you
OL,12,     Fdo more with less!
OL,13,G0730 JML Presents
OL,14,     FShop JML, the home for clever
OL,15,     Fideas.
OL,16,G0800 Bargain-Loving Brits in the Sun
OL,17,     FWe join Wiganers and charity
OL,18,     Fworkers Jane and Andy who
OL,19,     Fvolunteer at a nearby donkey
OL,20,     Fsanctuary. They are hoping to
OL,21,     Fcombine two passions: charity work
OL,22,     Fwith cooking.
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
