OL,5,G2100 Ambulance: Code Red
OL,6,     FAn air ambulance is sent to help a
OL,7,     Ftree surgeon impaled on metal
OL,8,     Frailings; a 6-year-old is rushed
OL,9,     Fto hospital for head injuries; a
OL,10,     Fdouble amputee is found lying in a
OL,11,     Fpool of blood.
OL,12,G2200 A&E After Dark
OL,13,     FAn aggressive patient is
OL,14,     Frestrained in Newham as Dr Nick
OL,15,     Forders ketamine sedation for a
OL,16,     Fhead injury. In Belfast, teenager
OL,17,     FJack suffers spinal shock after a
OL,18,     Fhorrific motorcycle crash.
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
